::Aerotaur::
    "Are you okay little one?"  He asks Trinity as he looks again at the 
battle.  "You should not be out here," he says and gallops back toward the 
Arc still carrying her.  At the Arc he goes inside, having seen nothing 
useful for himself to do.  He looks around and asks loudly "Who is in charge 
here?  I must speak to you now."
